name: Brainstorming UI Style Kit
description:
Brainstorming - UI Style kit. Trendy design that you can use for inspiration for your app with super quality design. Each screen is fully customizable, exceptionally easy to use and carefully layered and grouped in FIGMA. It's all you need for a quick prototype, design.
⁣
𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝘀𝘆𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗺 𝗶𝗻𝗰𝗹𝘂𝗱𝗲𝘀:⁣
- 16 style categories
- 149 different styles⁣
- 21 screen categorie
- 235 screens
- 680 components
⁣
Tons of handcrafted components and screens created to increase your app creating speed, for Figma. We've chosen the bright color palette that arouses only positive emotions and is sure to be loved by almost everyone. All components are nicely organized and named for better search and use.
